{"type": "article", "id": 14726, "title": "哈利·波特超级精装版发售，以及，爱马仕发了苹果表……带｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-09-10T09:13:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 15846, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 8845, "name": "摄影展"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 15847, "name": "CITIZEN"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 15848, "name": "Evian"}, {"id": 15849, "name": "Time.Inc"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605221031aUPifl8n5Dsd1hMX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\t一些重要的新闻：\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/time-ecommerce-people-style-travel-leisure-10212781/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Time 出版集团推出电商计划</strong></a><span>｜纽约出版集团 Time 将旗下的 </span><em>People</em><span> 和《悦旅》（ </span><em>Travel + Leisure </em><span> ）整合出新的可购买战略。</span><em> People</em><span> 增添 Style 板块，以提供新闻、视频和可购买的内容关注名人的造型，同时拉动广告量。而 </span><em>Travel + Leisure </em><span>是与高端旅行机构 Black Tomato 合作，推出一系列定制旅游路线、计划等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Supreme-quietly-reveals-new-design-director-Max-Vanderwoude-Gross,567752.html\" target=\"_blank\">Supreme 任命新创意总监</a></strong>｜看来 Supreme 已经找到了新的设计师，各路媒体“Max Vanderwoude Gross 为人选”的猜测成真。Gross 2012 年创立自己的品牌 Proper Gang，他会在前总监 Brendon Babenzien 最后的春款产品上线后上任。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1441769045327.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>优衣库进军第 5 个欧洲市场比利时</strong></a>｜亚洲最大服装零售商迅销集团（ Fast Retailing Co. Ltd.）昨日宣布旗下优衣库品牌 Uniqlo 即将进军第 5 个欧洲市场，于 10 月 2 日在比利时安特卫普开设面积达 1320 平方米的旗舰店。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/tommy-hilfiger-sets-exhibition-rock-style-at-sothebys-gallery-in-london-10212194/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tommy Hilfiger 在伦敦开 “Rock Style” 展览</strong></a>｜9 月22－10 月30 日，设计师 Tommy Hilfiger  与美国著名策展人 Jeffrey Deitch 一同策划了一场名为 “Rock Style” 的展览，在苏富比 Sotheby 画廊。力图通过上世纪著名的歌手和乐队——如滚石乐队、披头士、麦当娜等人的照片来解释设计、音乐与摄影之间的关联。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1441725468129.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>马莎百货表示中国市场仍是集团国际焦点</strong></a>｜Marks &amp; Spencer 面对当前中国经济放缓、消费意欲疲软，不得不放低对中国市场的预期。周二，M&amp;S 营销和国际总监 Patrick Bousquet-Chavanne 在接受<a href=\"http://uk.reuters.com/article/2015/09/08/uk-marks-spencer-international-idUKKCN0R813H20150908\">路透社</a>采访时坦言将放缓国际市场扩张，不过他同时表示俄罗斯、中国市场仍是该集团全球扩张的重点。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\t一些值得一看的：\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t爱玩跨界的 Alexander Wang 设计了限定<a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Alexander-Wang-collaborates-with-Evian-on-water-bottle-design,568442.html\" target=\"_blank\">依云（Evian）矿泉水瓶</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Alexander-Wang-collaborates-with-Evian-on-water-bottle-design,568442.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220958yHm2gi4YDEx5c6lp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.apple.com/apple-watch-hermes/\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Watch 将出 Hermès 款</a>，三种款式，最低价为 1100 美元。官网显示将于 2015 年 10 月发售，可以在苹果店和爱马仕门店购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220959vqcsSIzKVrmFGt1R.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060522095985jIka2QNyUfs1oh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66797258\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221000sAci847jPheRoraf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221000lfHboWC6NehRAxa0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221001mKbOwCXoi68u5sLn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tCITIZEN 旗下针对年轻市场的潮流子品牌 Q&amp;Q SmileSolar 即将于 10 月<a href=\"http://popbee.cn/accessories/watches/citizen-qq-limited-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">推出「The RED LIST」与「The Great Men」两个限定系列</a>手表。分别将 7 种濒危野生动物的纹理和 5 位名人所说的名言以及他们的肖像绘制在表带上。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221001KzULF9Mf4Zwtl3nj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221002y5TdWOZ7gx32AlCI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://en.vogue.fr/fashion/fashion-shopping/diaporama/the-boombox-graffiti-bag-by-moschino/22282#le-sac-boombox-graffiti-de-moschino\" target=\"_blank\">Moschino 布满涂鸦的手提收音机式包</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://en.vogue.fr/fashion/fashion-shopping/diaporama/the-boombox-graffiti-bag-by-moschino/22282#le-sac-boombox-graffiti-de-moschino\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221004cmhR0CG7KLfsdaVX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.93587174\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tChloé 推出 4 款粉嫩圣诞限定香水礼盒\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221004lzuioE3pLtbhc8yd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052210050CDYmizABVwTUP5F.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221005x9WrsLp0XJTe3mzt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221006tuanQGgiKYqxDIzl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://nowre.com/news/6512/puma-x-mcq-2015-qiu-dong-shi-pin-lookbook\" target=\"_blank\">PUMA 和 McQ 的秋冬季联名系列最新 Lookbook 释出</a>，迷幻风格的照片黑白为主，炫彩点缀。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052210062UwrliXTYdaVftIu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59968603\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221007CIYKFOwgVbBG15fz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59968603\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221007Fpi9qoz37XdZlfvG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59968603\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221008fVzOHASF1DKgnMo0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59968603\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221009swnikdq1tIUhOxVp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59968603\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t哈利·波特周边迷也许会 high──最近 <span style=\"text-align:left;\">juniper</span> Books 出版社出版了<a href=\"http://juniperbooks.com/store/harry-potter-sets/\" target=\"_blank\">完整 7 本《哈利·波特》的精装版</a>，定价 275 美金。而且还按照四大校园分为不同颜色，橙色版－Gryffindor 代表勇敢无畏、黄色版－Hufflepuff 代表刚正不阿、蓝色版－Ravenclaw 代表聪慧机智、绿色版 Slytherin－代表野心狡猾。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221023MVAzUZlRhDv5jFkb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80492091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221023DjxOrW3PJ6Z4mKBV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83044983\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221024Qy38pl9AgfTVcudN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00746269\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052210253hxYBs9wjyqv7EQr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02697495\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2015/9/givenchy-2015-fall-winter-lookbook\" target=\"_blank\">Givenchy 2015 秋冬季新款造型</a>：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221025UvaK18Sh6gHZbN4T.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221027tUeBFw8jypZq26Yd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221027wc2GPSOi3fmbuMz9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605221029KpXkPQw1bJ6BtW5C.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}